Package: ros-hydro-openni-camera
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, liblog4cxx10-dev, libopenni-dev, libopenni-sensor-primesense-dev, libusb-1.0-0-dev, ros-hydro-camera-info-manager, ros-hydro-dynamic-reconfigure, ros-hydro-image-transport, ros-hydro-nodelet, ros-hydro-roscpp, ros-hydro-sensor-msgs
Description: A ROS driver for OpenNI depth (+ RGB) cameras. These include: Microsoft Kinect, PrimeSense PSDK, ASUS Xtion Pro and Pro Live The driver publishes raw depth, RGB, and IR image streams.
